# CODEOWNERS — epam-claude-marketplace
#
# Two-tier review model:
#   - Root files and marketplace.json → marketplace owner (@spadhy) + designated reviewers
#   - Plugin folders → that plugin's named maintainer
#
# Designated reviewers (empowered to approve PRs alongside @spadhy):
#   @spadhy          — Marketplace owner
#   @[REVIEWER_2]    — Replace with second practice lead's GitHub handle
#   @[REVIEWER_3]    — Replace with third practice lead's GitHub handle
#
# Format: /path/  @github-handle
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Marketplace root — all changes require marketplace owner + a designated reviewer
*                                    @spadhy @[REVIEWER_2]
/.claude-plugin/                     @spadhy @[REVIEWER_2]
/README.md                           @spadhy @[REVIEWER_2]
/CONTRIBUTING.md                     @spadhy @[REVIEWER_2]
/CODEOWNERS                          @spadhy @[REVIEWER_2]

# Plugins — each plugin owned by its named maintainer
# (replace @spadhy with the actual maintainer handle when a new owner takes over)
/plugins/attention-today/            @spadhy
/plugins/team-progress/              @spadhy
/plugins/salesforce-solution-design/ @spadhy
/plugins/meeting-brief-agent/        @spadhy
